text: Ted Cruz (born 1970) is a U.S. Senator from Texas since 2013. Senator Cruz may refer to: *Benjamin Cruz (born 1951), Senate of Guam *Donovan Dela Cruz (born 1973), Hawaii State Senate *Michael Cruz (born 1958), Senate of Guam *Nilsa Cruz-Perez (born 1961), New Jersey State Senate
title: Senator Cruz (disambiguation)
